DIRECTORS' ASSOCIATION.

18:13.326 --> 18:15.428
MARK WOLFE, HOW SIGNIFICANT IS

18:15.428 --> 18:17.396
FUEL INSECURITY IN THESE WINTER

18:17.396 --> 18:18.931
MONTHS?

