22:41.460 --> 22:42.294
>> Reporter: MALARIA IS ONE OF

22:42.294 --> 22:43.495
THE WORLD'S MOST DEADLY

22:43.495 --> 22:44.730
DISEASES.

22:44.730 --> 22:46.131
CAUSED BY A PARASITE SPREAD BY

22:46.131 --> 22:48.801
MOSQUITOES, IT INFECTED 200

22:48.801 --> 22:50.803
MILLION PEOPLE LAST YEAR ALONE

22:50.803 --> 22:53.305
AND KILLED OVER 600,000.

22:53.305 --> 22:54.607
VACCINES AND DRUGS THAT WERE

22:54.607 --> 22:55.874
USED TO FIGHT THE PARASITE IN

22:55.874 --> 22:58.110
THE MID-20th CENTURY SOON BECAME

22:58.110 --> 22:59.878
USELESS AS THE BUG DEVELOPED

22:59.878 --> 23:01.513
RESISTANCE.

23:01.513 --> 23:03.182
A NEW DRUG, ARTEMISININ, GAVE

23:03.182 --> 23:05.351
HOPE IN RECENT DECADES, BUT NEW

23:05.351 --> 23:07.086
RESEARCH SHOWS THAT THAT, TOO,

23:07.086 --> 23:08.754
IS LOSING ITS POWER.

23:08.754 --> 23:10.356
>> WE NOW KNOW PART OF THE

23:10.356 --> 23:12.024
MOLECULAR MACHINERY OF THE

23:12.024 --> 23:14.994
PARASITE THAT WORKS TO OVERCOME

23:14.994 --> 23:16.061
THIS DRUG.

23:16.061 --> 23:17.329
>> Reporter: IN 2005,

23:17.329 --> 23:19.431
