23:31.343 --> 23:33.312
SHOWS THAT THE RESISTANCE IS NOW

23:33.312 --> 23:35.347
PREVALENT IN MYANMAR, AND CASES

23:35.347 --> 23:37.850
HAVE APPEARED JUST 15 MILES FROM

23:37.850 --> 23:39.184
THE INDIAN BORDER.

23:39.184 --> 23:41.153
IF THE SPREAD CONTINUES AND

23:41.153 --> 23:43.322
REACHES INDIA OR AFRICA, THE

23:43.322 --> 23:45.157
CONSEQUENCES WOULD BE DIRE.

23:45.157 --> 23:46.258
>> I THINK IT'S ABSOLUTELY

23:46.258 --> 23:48.360
IMPERATIVE THAT WE GET ON TOP OF

23:48.360 --> 23:49.228
THIS.

